{
  "translationLines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 229232,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "案内してくれていた兵士が、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "The soldier who had been guiding us,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229233,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "気さくに話しかけてきた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "casually started talking."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229234,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「プレジデント・シーラは、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"President Sheila has"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229235,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　以前より皆様に会えるのを",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "been looking forward to meeting all of you"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229236,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　それは楽しみにしてましたから」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "for quite some time.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229237,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「さ、大統領はこちらの部屋に」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Now, the President is in this room.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229238,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「うお、やべっ、ついにか！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Whoa, oh man, it's finally happening!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229239,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「大統領、皆様がおつきになりました」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"President, everyone has arrived.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229240,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "兵士のノックの後、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "After the soldier knocked,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229241,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "室内から綺麗な声がこちらまで届いた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "a beautiful voice came from inside the room."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229242,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「分かりました、どうぞ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Understood, please come in.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229243,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「はい。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Yes."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229244,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　失礼します」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Excuse us.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229245,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "あなた達は少し緊張しながら、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "You felt a little nervous as"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229246,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ゆっくりと大統領執務室への扉を開けた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "you slowly opened the door to the President's office."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229247,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あっ……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ah...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229248,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "室内にいた女性があなた達に振り返る。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "The woman inside turned to look at you."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229249,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "（うおっ、綺麗な人だなぁ）",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "(Wow, she's beautiful.)"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229250,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "陽光を浴びてたなびく金髪が",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Her blonde hair fluttering in the sunlight"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229251,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "キラキラと光を反射させていた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "sparkled and reflected the light."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229252,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ああっ、みんな、いらっしゃい」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ah, everyone, welcome!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229253,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あ、あれ？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Huh, huh?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229254,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「さあさあ、長旅で疲れたでしょう？",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Come, come, you must be tired from the long journey?"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229255,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　早く座って、座って。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Please sit down quickly, sit down."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229256,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　今お茶淹れますからね」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I'll make some tea right now.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229257,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "テーブルの上にはシーラ大統領が用意したらしき、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "On the table were tea and light snacks that President Sheila seemed to have prepared."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229258,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "お茶と軽食がズラリと並べられていた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "They were neatly laid out in a row."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229259,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あ、あの、シーラ様……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ah, um, Lady Sheila..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229260,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　そういうことは私が……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I should be the one to do those things...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229261,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ううん、いいの、いいの。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"No, it's okay, it's okay."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229262,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　私がしたいんだから、任せて、ね？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I want to do it, so leave it to me, okay?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229263,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あ、ああ、もう……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ah, ah, geez...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229264,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "メイドが止めようとするのを制して、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Stopping the maid who tried to intervene,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229265,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "大統領はうきうきしながら、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "the President cheerfully"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229266,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "いそいそとお茶を淹れていた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "hurriedly brewed the tea."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229267,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ほらほら、みんなどうしたの？",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Now, now, what's wrong everyone?"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229268,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　遠慮なんてしなくていいんですからね」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "You don't have to be so reserved.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229269,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「……友達ん家の",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"...She's like a super friendly mom at a friend's house."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229270,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　めっちゃ気さくなお母さんみたいな人だ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": ""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229271,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ふふふ、だから言ったでしょー？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Hehe, didn't I tell you so?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229272,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「変わんねーな、この人も……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"This person hasn't changed at all...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229273,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「それじゃあ、改めて……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Well then, once again...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229274,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「…………」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"........\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229275,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ふふ……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Hehe..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229276,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　みんな、いらっしゃい」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Welcome, everyone.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229277,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "穏やかな微笑みをたたえて、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "With a gentle smile,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229278,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "大統領、シーラ・ヘルマンはあなた達を迎えた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "President Sheila Herman greeted you."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229279,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "あなた達は執務室にある、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "You sat on the large sofa in the office,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229280,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "大きなソファに座りながら、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": ""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229281,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "大統領手ずから淹れてくれたお茶を飲んでいた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "drinking the tea personally brewed by the President."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229282,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ふふ、それにしても、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Hehe, even so,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229283,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　皆さん元気そうで安心した」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I'm relieved to see you all looking well.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229284,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「それに、こんな大きく、立派になって……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"And you've all grown so big and splendid...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229285,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「っ……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229286,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　本当に、みんな大きくなりましたね」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "You really have all grown up.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229287,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "じわり。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "*Slowly.*"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229288,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "シーラの瞳に涙が浮かぶ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Tears welled up in Sheila's eyes."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229289,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「本当に……よく頑張って……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Truly... you've done so well...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229290,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「やめろ……うっとうしい」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Stop it... It's annoying.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229291,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あ、うん、ごめんね。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ah, yeah, sorry.\""
    }
  ]
}

